reviewText: My grandchildren enjoyed 'The Swan Princess And The Secret Of The Castle' so much that this seemed to be a fun last adventure. The same animated characters with the addition of a wicked sorceress.  Secrets revealed and secrets that must be destroyed before they destroy everyone! Definitely recommended for those who enjoyed the first in the series (offered with prime) and grandchild approved!Purchased as an instant video and stored on Amazon . . . smooth streaming and crisp audio.

reviewText: This movie wasn't the best of the three, but it was very cute. The characters are pretty good in addition to the new bird character. It is good for young kids, not really older audiences, but if you liked the first one, this one should pass fairly well. I liked it.
